# D-L-Interiors-LLC
We Offer Affordable Professional Interior Services
When it comes to enhancing the beauty, comfort, and value of your home or commercial space, quality interior work makes all the difference. D & L Interiors, LLC is a trusted interior service provider proudly serving Ellington, Somers, South Windsor, and the greater Tolland County area. With a strong focus on craftsmanship, attention to detail, and customer satisfaction, the company delivers interior solutions that are both durable and visually appealing.

Whether you are planning a full interior refresh or need targeted repairs, D & L Interiors, LLC offers professional services designed to meet your needs and exceed expectations.

Professional Interior Painting Services

A fresh coat of paint can completely transform a space. D & L Interiors, LLC specializes in interior painting services that enhance the look and feel of any room. From subtle, modern tones to bold, expressive colors, their team works closely with clients to achieve the desired finish.

Every painting project is handled with precision, from proper surface preparation to clean, even application. The result is a smooth, long-lasting finish that elevates interiors while protecting walls from wear and tear. Whether it’s a single room or an entire property, their painting services add instant value and style.

Popcorn Ceiling Removal and Repair

Outdated popcorn ceilings can make a space feel dark and dated. D & L Interiors, LLC provides professional popcorn ceiling removal to help homeowners achieve a cleaner, more modern look. The team uses safe and efficient techniques to remove textured ceilings while minimizing mess and disruption.

In cases where ceilings have been damaged or partially removed, their popcorn ceiling repair services restore surfaces to a smooth, consistent finish. This attention to detail ensures the ceiling blends seamlessly with the rest of the space, creating a polished and updated appearance.

Drywall Installation and Repair

Strong, well-installed drywall is the foundation of any interior space. D & L Interiors, LLC offers reliable drywall installation and repair services for both residential and commercial properties. From new construction projects to patching holes, cracks, and water damage, their team ensures walls and ceilings are structurally sound and visually flawless.

Each drywall project is completed with careful measurement, clean finishing, and proper sanding to prepare surfaces for painting or texturing. The result is a smooth, professional finish built to last.

Acoustic Ceiling Installation

For spaces that require improved sound control and a clean, functional design, D & L Interiors, LLC provides acoustic ceiling installation services. These ceilings are ideal for offices, commercial buildings, basements, and multi-purpose rooms where noise reduction and aesthetics matter.

The team installs acoustic ceilings with precision, ensuring proper alignment and durability. This service not only improves sound quality but also enhances the overall appearance and functionality of the space.

Serving Ellington, Somers, South Windsor, and Tolland County

D & L Interiors, LLC is proud to serve homeowners and businesses throughout Ellington, Somers, South Windsor, and surrounding areas in Tolland County. Their local expertise allows them to understand the needs of the community and provide personalized service with reliable timelines and clear communication.

Clients appreciate their commitment to professionalism, honest pricing, and high-quality results on every project, regardless of size or complexity.

